{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"The AlloSphere: it's a three-story metal sphere"},{"time":3000,"text":"in an echo-free chamber."},{"time":5000,"text":"Think of the AlloSphere as a large,"},{"time":7000,"text":"dynamically varying digital microscope"},{"time":10000,"text":"that's connected to a supercomputer."},{"time":12000,"text":"20 researchers can stand on a bridge"},{"time":15000,"text":"suspended inside of the sphere, and be"},{"time":17000,"text":"completely immersed in their data."}]},{"cues":[{"time":19000,"text":"Imagine if a team of physicists"},{"time":21000,"text":"could stand inside of an atom"},{"time":24000,"text":"and watch and hear electrons spin."},{"time":26000,"text":"Imagine if a group of sculptors"},{"time":30000,"text":"could be inside of a lattice of atoms"},{"time":33000,"text":"and sculpt with their material."},{"time":35000,"text":"Imagine if a team of surgeons could fly"},{"time":37000,"text":"into the brain, as though it was a world,"},{"time":40000,"text":"and see tissues as landscapes,"},{"time":42000,"text":"and hear blood density levels as music."},{"time":45000,"text":"This is some of the research that you're going to see"},{"time":47000,"text":"that we're undertaking at the AlloSphere."}]},{"cues":[{"time":49000,"text":"But first a little bit about this group"},{"time":51000,"text":"of artists, scientists, and engineers"},{"time":53000,"text":"that are working together."},{"time":55000,"text":"I'm a composer, orchestrally-trained,"},{"time":57000,"text":"and the inventor of the AlloSphere."},{"time":59000,"text":"With my visual artist colleagues, we map"},{"time":61000,"text":"complex mathematical algorithms that unfold in time and space,"},{"time":64000,"text":"visually and sonically."},{"time":66000,"text":"Our scientist colleagues are finding new patterns"},{"time":68000,"text":"in the information."},{"time":70000,"text":"And our engineering colleagues are making"},{"time":72000,"text":"one of the largest dynamically varying computers in the world"},{"time":76000,"text":"for this kind of data exploration."},{"time":78000,"text":"I'm going to fly you into five research projects"},{"time":81000,"text":"in the AlloSphere that are going to take you from"},{"time":83000,"text":"biological macroscopic data"},{"time":85000,"text":"all the way down to electron spin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":88000,"text":"This first project is called the AlloBrain."},{"time":91000,"text":"And it's our attempt to quantify beauty"},{"time":93000,"text":"by finding which regions of the brain"},{"time":95000,"text":"are interactive while witnessing something beautiful."},{"time":99000,"text":"You're flying through the cortex of my colleague's brain."},{"time":102000,"text":"Our narrative here is real fMRI data"},{"time":105000,"text":"that's mapped visually and sonically."},{"time":107000,"text":"The brain now a world that we can fly through and interact with."},{"time":111000,"text":"You see 12 intelligent computer agents,"},{"time":114000,"text":"the little rectangles that are flying in the brain with you."},{"time":117000,"text":"They're mining blood density levels."},{"time":119000,"text":"And they're reporting them back to you sonically."},{"time":122000,"text":"Higher density levels mean"},{"time":124000,"text":"more activity in that point of the brain."},{"time":126000,"text":"They're actually singing these densities to you"},{"time":129000,"text":"with higher pitches mapped to higher densities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":132000,"text":"We're now going to move from real biological data"},{"time":135000,"text":"to biogenerative algorithms that create artificial nature"},{"time":139000,"text":"in our next artistic and scientific installation."},{"time":143000,"text":"In this artistic and scientific installation, biogenerative algorithms"},{"time":147000,"text":"are helping us to understand"},{"time":149000,"text":"self-generation and growth:"},{"time":151000,"text":"very important for simulation in the nanoscaled sciences."},{"time":155000,"text":"For artists, we're making new worlds"},{"time":157000,"text":"that we can uncover and explore."},{"time":159000,"text":"These generative algorithms grow over time,"},{"time":162000,"text":"and they interact and communicate as a swarm of insects."},{"time":165000,"text":"Our researchers are interacting with this data"},{"time":167000,"text":"by injecting bacterial code,"},{"time":169000,"text":"which are computer programs,"},{"time":171000,"text":"that allow these creatures to grow over time."},{"time":175000,"text":"We're going to move now from the biological"},{"time":177000,"text":"and the macroscopic world,"},{"time":179000,"text":"down into the atomic world,"},{"time":181000,"text":"as we fly into a lattice of atoms."},{"time":184000,"text":"This is real AFM -- Atomic Force Microscope -- data"},{"time":187000,"text":"from my colleagues in the Solid State Lighting and Energy Center."},{"time":190000,"text":"They've discovered a new bond,"},{"time":192000,"text":"a new material for transparent solar cells."}]},{"cues":[{"time":195000,"text":"We're flying through 2,000 lattice of atoms --"},{"time":198000,"text":"oxygen, hydrogen and zinc."},{"time":200000,"text":"You view the bond in the triangle."},{"time":203000,"text":"It's four blue zinc atoms"},{"time":205000,"text":"bonding with one white hydrogen atom."},{"time":208000,"text":"You see the electron flow with the streamlines"},{"time":210000,"text":"we as artists have generated for the scientists."},{"time":213000,"text":"This is allowing them to find the bonding nodes in any lattice of atoms."},{"time":216000,"text":"We think it makes a beautiful structural art."},{"time":219000,"text":"The sound that you're hearing are the actual"},{"time":221000,"text":"emission spectrums of these atoms."},{"time":223000,"text":"We've mapped them into the audio domain,"},{"time":225000,"text":"so they're singing to you."},{"time":227000,"text":"Oxygen, hydrogen and zinc have their own signature."},{"time":230000,"text":"We're going to actually move even further down"},{"time":233000,"text":"as we go from this lattice of atoms"},{"time":236000,"text":"to one single hydrogen atom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":239000,"text":"We're working with our physicist colleagues"},{"time":241000,"text":"that have given us the mathematical calculations"},{"time":244000,"text":"of the n-dimensional Schr√∂dinger equation in time."},{"time":248000,"text":"What you're seeing here right now is a superposition of an electron"},{"time":251000,"text":"in the lower three orbitals of a hydrogen atom."},{"time":254000,"text":"You're actually hearing and seeing the electron flow with the lines."},{"time":258000,"text":"The white dots are the probability wave"},{"time":260000,"text":"that will show you where the electron is"},{"time":262000,"text":"in any given point of time and space"},{"time":264000,"text":"in this particular three-orbital configuration."},{"time":268000,"text":"In a minute we're going to move to a two-orbital configuration,"},{"time":272000,"text":"and you're going to notice a pulsing."},{"time":274000,"text":"And you're going to hear an undulation between the sound."},{"time":277000,"text":"This is actually a light emitter."},{"time":279000,"text":"As the sound starts to pulse and contract,"},{"time":282000,"text":"our physicists can tell when a photon is going to be emitted."}]},{"cues":[{"time":285000,"text":"They're starting to find new mathematical structures"},{"time":289000,"text":"in these calculations."},{"time":291000,"text":"And they're understanding more about quantum mathematics."},{"time":294000,"text":"We're going to move even further down,"},{"time":297000,"text":"and go to one single electron spin."},{"time":301000,"text":"This will be the final project that I show you."},{"time":304000,"text":"Our colleagues in the Center for Quantum Computation"},{"time":306000,"text":"and Spintronics are actually measuring with their lasers"},{"time":310000,"text":"decoherence in a single electron spin."},{"time":313000,"text":"We've taken this information and we've"},{"time":315000,"text":"made a mathematical model out of it."},{"time":317000,"text":"You're actually seeing and hearing"},{"time":319000,"text":"quantum information flow."},{"time":321000,"text":"This is very important for the next step in simulating"},{"time":324000,"text":"quantum computers and information technology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":327000,"text":"So these brief examples that I've shown you"},{"time":331000,"text":"give you an idea of the kind of work that we're doing"},{"time":334000,"text":"at the University of California, Santa Barbara,"},{"time":336000,"text":"to bring together, arts, science"},{"time":339000,"text":"and engineering"},{"time":342000,"text":"into a new age of math, science and art."},{"time":345000,"text":"We hope that all of you will come to see the AlloSphere."},{"time":348000,"text":"Inspire us to think of new ways that we can use"},{"time":352000,"text":"this unique instrument that we've created at Santa Barbara."},{"time":356000,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":358000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}